        Selling a Brisbane Townhouse: How the Market and Process Differ
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A Brisbane townhouse is not priced, marketed, or sold the same way as a house or an apartment. Understanding the differences makes for a more realistic campaign and a stronger result.
      </p>
